This is an asynchronous API. You will get a Build Id as a response. To know when the build has ended, you should call the “Get Builds Status of a Model” API and locate this build Id in the response. Note that a build can take from minutes to hours depending on the size of the data. You cannot consume recommendations till the build ends.
Valid build status:
* Create – model was created * Queued – model build was triggered and it is queued * Building – the model is being build * Success – the build ended successfully * Error – the build ended with a failure * Cancelled – build was canceled * Cancelling – build is being cancelled
Feed\entry\content\properties\Id – contains the build id
